author: @patricemelvinciccone2930
content:
Hello, thanks for sharing - let's never forget! When AIDS ravaged our Gay Brothers 🏳‍🌈, the whole world remained silent.
But Madonna 👑, tireless activist, did not remain silent.
While the other artists were silent 🤮 🙈💩
Madonna👑 offered comfort to our Brothers 🏳‍🌈 hugging them, comforting them and staying with them so that they do not face their last moments alone.
Glory to Madonna👑 for her exceptional human qualities.
